      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from how it first rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with no scratches, dents, or swirl marks, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. A buyer can expect a car that looks and drives like new, requiring absolutely no immediate attention or repairs.",
