    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. Can\u2019t wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1), a purist\u2019s specification featuring the 3.6L M96/05 flat-six and the desirable G97 6-speed manual transaxle. This example maintains its communicative hydraulic steering and features a documented IMS bearing retrofit for long-term reliability. The engine pulls strongly through the rev range with no bore scoring symptoms, and the gear shifts are tight and precise. The chassis remains composed with a multi-link rear suspension setup that provides excellent lateral stability. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and ventilated rotors, the braking system offers firm pedal feel and consistent thermal management. A true driver's car that balances analog feedback with modern refinement.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously cared-for example that perfectly bridges the gap between a daily driver and a luxury cruiser. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a vehicle that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are soft and intact, with minimal wear confined to the driver-side entry point. Every button, dial, and digital display operates flawlessly, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Under the hood, the powertrain is robust, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. The transmission shifts are smooth and predictable, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a quiet and stable ride for the foreseeable future. This car represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with pride of ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated blend of performance and long-term reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain, it stands as a premier choice for the driver who demands quality and consistency. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that has been curated for the discerning professional.",
      "price": 34800.0,
