      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! It's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
